rComments: The amount of work and readings you have to put in after the lectures is tremendous. You will likely be tested on everything that is included in the slides and readings, so don't skip anything. Do no worry, Professor Li is generous and gives you past midterms and exams that are very similar to what you will be tested on.
teacherRatingTags: ['Graded by few things', 'Test heavy', 'Get ready to read']
